text: H is the eighth (number 8) letter in the English alphabet. The uppercase letter for H name is "haitch" (), also known as simply "'aitch" (). == Meanings for H == * In chemistry, H is the symbol for hydrogen. * In music, H is a note in the German system, meaning "B natural". * In particle physics, H is the symbol for the Higgs boson. ==Other websites==
